<p><b>April 22 Earth Day</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.earthiness.info/" class="external text" title="http://www.earthiness.info/" rel="nofollow">Earth Day Website</a> - Community website on Earth Day.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.earthday.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.earthday.net/" rel="nofollow">Earth Day Network</a> - Coordinating worldwide events for Earth Day.</li>
<li><a href="http://earthday.envirolink.org" class="external text" title="http://earthday.envirolink.org" rel="nofollow">Earth Day Event Calendar</a> at the <a href="/wiki/EnviroLink_Network" title="EnviroLink Network">EnviroLink Network</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.wikihow.com/Celebrate-Earth-Day" class="external text" title="http://www.wikihow.com/Celebrate-Earth-Day" rel="nofollow">Celebrate Earth Day</a> How to Celebrate Earth Day from <a href="/wiki/WikiHow" title="WikiHow">WikiHow</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.earthday.gov/" class="external text" title="http://www.earthday.gov/" rel="nofollow">United States Earth Day</a> - The U.S. government's <i>Earth Day</i> site.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.earthday.ca/" class="external text" title="http://www.earthday.ca/" rel="nofollow">Earth Day Canada</a> - The Canadian Official Site for <i>Earth Day</i></li>
<li><a href="http://www.kab.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.kab.org/" rel="nofollow">Keep America Beautiful</a> - Keep America Beautiful holds Earth Day cleanup activities in communities nationwide. The organization launched the famous <a href="/wiki/Crying_Indian" title="Crying Indian" class="mw-redirect">Crying Indian</a> campaign on Earth Day, 1971.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.dhammakaya.or.th/events/490422_earthday.php" class="external text" title="http://www.dhammakaya.or.th/events/490422_earthday.php" rel="nofollow">Earth Day at Dhammakaya Temple</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.lessonplanet.com/curriculum_connections/science_lesson_plans/25_March_2009/17/earth_day_lessons_with_the_right_stuff?frm=PREarthday" class="external text" title="http://www.lessonplanet.com/curriculum_connections/science_lesson_plans/25_March_2009/17/earth_day_lessons_with_the_right_stuff?frm=PREarthday" rel="nofollow">Earth Day Lesson Plans and Learning Resources</a></li>
</ul>
